snippet.title: Bakra Nahi Majnu Halaal - Part 2 : Full On Farziwada - Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Download Skkily Ludo App From 
https://bit.ly/Amit-bhadana

REFERRAL CODE - AMIT100


Jab aag lagi hai to dhamaka to ho kar rahega. Hamare Majnu ne le lie hain bade wala panga. 2 ladkiyon ko date toh bahut log karte hain lekin hamara hero 2 sagi behnon se pyar kar baitha hani. Lalach buri bala hain Rinku na Raveena se breakup karna chahata hai aur na hi Sangeeta ko ta-ta bye-bye, aur ab vo galti se pahunch gaya hain dono ke ghar jahan bas phootne hi wala hai uska bhaanda. Kya hoga aage isi baat ka hai sabko intezaar. Kya Sangeeta aur Raveena mil kar karengi Rinku ko halal ya unke papa karenge hamare Majnu ka kaam tamaam? Kya hoga is love story ka end? Ye sab pata chalega is part mein. To sab mil kar hamare Majnu ke lie prarthna karo aur poore parivaar family ke sath dekho ye kamaal dhamaal story. Dhnyaawad :)

snippet.title: FARZI - Official Trailer | Raj & DK | Shahid, Sethupathi, Kay Kay, Raashii | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video presents
FARZI Official Hindi Trailer 

Starring Shahid Kapoor, Vijay Sethupathi, Kay Kay Menon, Raashii Khanna, Bhuvan Arora, Zakir Hussain, Chittranjan Giri, Jaswant Singh Dalal AND Amol Palekar and Kubbra Sait and Regina Cassandra. 

Created and Directed by Raj & DK
Written by Raj & DK, Sita R Menon, Suman Kumar
Produced by D2R Films

Release date : Feb 10, 2023 On Prime Video India

About : 
Sunny, a brilliant small-time artist is catapulted into the high-stakes world of counterfeiting when he creates the perfect fake currency note, even as Michael, a fiery, unorthodox task force officer wants to rid the country of the counterfeiting menace. In this thrilling cat-and-mouse race, losing is not an option!

About Prime Video
Prime Video is a premium streaming service that offers Prime members a collection of award-winning Amazon Original series, thousands of movies and TV shows—all with the ease of finding what they love to watch in one place.  Find out more at PrimeVideo.com.

Included with Prime Video: 
Thousands of acclaimed TV shows and movies across languages and geographies, including Indian films such as Jai Bhim, Shershaah, Toofaan, Sardar Udham, Coolie No. 1, Gulabo Sitabo, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Durgamati, Chhalaang, Hello Charlie, Cold Case, Narappa, Sara’s, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi and Tuck Jagadish, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Mumbai Diaries 26/11, The Last Hour, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Breathe, Comicstaan Semma Comedy Pa, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Inside Edge and Made In Heaven. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like The Tomorrow War, Coming 2 America, Cinderella, Borat Subsequent Moviefilm, Without Remorse, The Wheel of Time, American Gods, One Night in Miami, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Cruel Summer, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel and many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi and Bengali.

Instant Access: 
Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV and multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid and post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices and tablets and watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.

Enhanced experiences
Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- and High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies and TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing.

snippet.title: DAMaN (In Hindi) Official Trailer | Babushaan Mohanty, Dipanwit D | In Cinemas 3rd February 2023
snippet.description:
In 2015, a young doctor, Dr. Siddharth Mohanty, who has just completed his MBBS from a government medical college, is posted  to a back of beyond tribal area in the Malkangiri district. Janbai PHC has 151 villages under it, is  infamous for its Naxal dominance and doesn't even boast of the most basic facilities. 
Dr. Siddharth Mohanty arrives reluctantly, wanting to quit at the earliest. But fate wills otherwise.  Daman is the story of 151 villages and one doctor to control the spread of malaria, the tussle between superstition and medical science. 

Presenting you the official trailer of DAMaN in Hindi.

#daman #damaninhindi

en-IN.title: DAMaN (In Hindi) Official Trailer | Babushaan Mohanty, Dipanwit D | In Cinemas 3rd February 2023
en-IN.description:
In 2015, a young doctor, Dr. Siddharth Mohanty, who has just completed his MBBS from a government medical college, is posted  to a back of beyond tribal area in the Malkangiri district. Janbai PHC has 151 villages under it, is  infamous for its Naxal dominance and doesn't even boast of the most basic facilities. 
Dr. Siddharth Mohanty arrives reluctantly, wanting to quit at the earliest. But fate wills otherwise.  Daman is the story of 151 villages and one doctor to control the spread of malaria, the tussle between superstition and medical science. 

Presenting you the official trailer of DAMaN in Hindi.

snippet.description:
बर्फ से लदे पहाड़ों से बहने वाली सर्द हवाएं आधे से ज्यादा हिंदुस्तान का तापमान गिराएंगी। राजस्थान में पारा शून्य से नीचे हरियाणा में भी शून्य के आसपास तापमान हो सकता है। 19 तारीख से नया पश्चिमी विक्षोभ पहाड़ों पर बर्फबारी देगा तथा मैदानी भागों के तापमान बढ़ने लगेंगे। 23 और 24 जनवरी से पंजाब हरियाणा उत्तर प्रदेश दिल्ली उत्तरी मध्य प्रदेश तथा उत्तरी राजस्थान में बारिश के आसार हैं।

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 06 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 06 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 12th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Yumna Zaidi as Meerab

snippet.title: Sweet Pongal Recipe in Tamil | Sakkarai Pongal Recipe in Tamil | Chakkarai Pongal
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make sweet pongal recipe in tamil. Sakkarai pongal is a great recipe which brings back so many warm memories, the soft fluffy cooked rice and dal with jaggery and roasted nuts is a great way to start the morning. This is pongal recipe is very easy to make and we can make pongal either in a pot or in a pressure cooker.


Sweet Pongal in pot :- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ESuqXoJj4M0
Sweet Pongal in cooker :- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AgWLO_cV7zw

Wish you all a very happy Pongal 2023 and have fun. Also, please do make this sweet pongal and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!

Ingredients:
1 cup Raw Rice
1/2 cup Moong Dal
1 cup Milk
1 cup rinsed Water
4.5-5 cup Water
2 cup Jaggery
4+4 tbsp Ghee
1/2 coconut pieces
1/4 cup Cashews
2 tbsp Raisins
1/2 tsp Cardamom
pinch of Salt

snippet.title: SYAAPA : EP 01 | COLLEGE RUSTICATE | KANGRA BOYS
snippet.description:
"SYAAPA" is Himachal's first ever web series produced by KANGRA BOYS

"SYAAPA" is the story of four friends and one of their senior advocate Makkhan. In this episode all four friends after being expelled from their college return to their ancestral house in their village. Here they encounter a dead body in their house and all of them are haunted by the fear that they might be accused of his murder. Now, they call one of their college senior advocate Makhan for help. Let's see how these four friends deal with this problem and if advocate Makkhan comes to help them.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 05 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 11th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

#vegthali #vegthalirecipes #completemeal #thalirecipes 

Today we are making bhogichi thali in Maharashtrian style. Bhogi is celebrated a day before Makar Sankranti.  On this day bhogichi bhaji or lukurwali bhaji, bajrichi bhakri with lots of sesame seeds, masale bhat or khichadi is made as naivedya. Bajri and sesame seeds provide necessary warmth to body. As lot many veggies are available in abundance so this lekurwali bhaji is made. This is a very healthy and delicious recipe. The thali looks nice and tastes just awesome. You can try this recipe at home and drop a comment for me. Do not forget to like, share and subscribe.

Ingredients:
Bhogichi Bhaji
• 1 tsp Oil
• 1 tsp Cumin seeds
• 1 tsp grated Ginger
• 1 tsp Goda masala
• 1 tsp Red chili powder
• 1/4 cup green flat Beans
• 1/4 cup Lima beans
• 1 chopped Vange
• 1 peeled and chopped Potato
• 4~5 Bor
• 1/4 cup fresh Peas
• 2~3 tsp Water
• Salt to taste
• Roasted Peanut powder
Bajrichi Bhakri
• Bajri flour
• Salt to taste
• Warm Water
• White Sesame seeds
Masale Bhat
• 1 tsp Oil
• 1 tsp Cumin seeds
• 1 Bay leaf
• 1 finely chopped Tomato
• 1 tsp grated Ginger
• 1 tsp Goda masala
• 1 tsp Red chili powder
• Turmeric powder
• 1 small peeled and chopped Potato
• Cauliflower florets
• Fresh peas 
• 1 cup whole Basmati rice
• 1 1/2 cup Water
• Salt to taste
• Few Cashew nuts
• 1 tsp Ghee

#vegthali #vegthalirecipes #completemeal #thalirecipes 

Today we are making bhogichi thali in Maharashtrian style. Bhogi is celebrated a day before Makar Sankranti.  On this day bhogichi bhaji or lukurwali bhaji, bajrichi bhakri with lots of sesame seeds, masale bhat or khichadi is made as naivedya. Bajri and sesame seeds provide necessary warmth to body. As lot many veggies are available in abundance so this lekurwali bhaji is made. This is a very healthy and delicious recipe. The thali looks nice and tastes just awesome. You can try this recipe at home and drop a comment for me. Do not forget to like, share and subscribe.

Ingredients:
Bhogichi Bhaji
• 1 tsp Oil
• 1 tsp Cumin seeds
• 1 tsp grated Ginger
• 1 tsp Goda masala
• 1 tsp Red chili powder
• 1/4 cup green flat Beans
• 1/4 cup Lima beans
• 1 chopped Vange
• 1 peeled and chopped Potato
• 4~5 Bor
• 1/4 cup fresh Peas
• 2~3 tsp Water
• Salt to taste
• Roasted Peanut powder
Bajrichi Bhakri
• Bajri flour
• Salt to taste
• Warm Water
• White Sesame seeds
Masale Bhat
• 1 tsp Oil
• 1 tsp Cumin seeds
• 1 Bay leaf
• 1 finely chopped Tomato
• 1 tsp grated Ginger
• 1 tsp Goda masala
• 1 tsp Red chili powder
• Turmeric powder
• 1 small peeled and chopped Potato
• Cauliflower florets
• Fresh peas 
• 1 cup whole Basmati rice
• 1 1/2 cup Water
• Salt to taste
• Few Cashew nuts
• 1 tsp Ghee

snippet.title: പ്രവീണ്‍ റാണയ്ക്ക് വിനയായത് നിക്ഷേപകരുടെ യോഗവും ആ വോയ്‌സ് ക്ലിപ്പും | Safe & Strong Fraud Case
snippet.description:
തൃശ്ശൂരിലെ സെയ്ഫ് ആന്‍ഡ് സ്‌ട്രോങ് നിക്ഷേപത്തട്ടിപ്പ് കേസില്‍ കമ്പനി എംഡി പ്രവീണ്‍ റാണയ്ക്ക് വിനയായത് നിക്ഷേപകരുടെ യോഗവും തുടര്‍ന്ന് അയച്ച വോയ്‌സ് ക്ലിപ്പും. വര്‍ഷങ്ങളോളം നൂറുകണക്കിന് നിക്ഷേപകരെ സമര്‍ത്ഥമായി പറ്റിച്ച റാണ, ഡിസംബര്‍ 27-ന് വിളിച്ച യോഗത്തിലൂടെ സ്വയം കുഴി തോണ്ടുകയായിരുന്നു. ഈ യോഗമാണ് വഞ്ചിക്കപ്പെട്ടവരുടെ കൂട്ടായ്മ രൂപീകരിക്കാനും തുടര്‍ന്ന് കേസുകള്‍ നല്‍കാനും കാരണമായതെന്ന് സെയ്ഫ് & സ്‌ട്രോങ് കസ്റ്റമര്‍ വെല്‍ഫെയര്‍ അസോസിയേഷന്‍ പ്രസിഡന്റ് രാജന്‍ ജോസഫ് പറയുന്നു.

#SweetRecipeInTamil #CarrotDelightRecipeByIndianRecipesTamil
#சுவீட் #CarrotSweet
#EasyQuickSweetTamil #10MinsSweetTamil
#3IngredientsSweet

இன்று இந்தியன் ரெசிபி தமிழில், கேரட்டின் மிகவும் புதிய, சுவையான  ரெசிபியை நான் கொண்டு வந்துள்ளேன், இது போன்ற சில விஷயங்களைக் கொண்ட அருமையான ரெசிபியை நீங்கள் பார்த்திருக்க மாட்டீர்கள், மேலும் இது மிகவும் எளிதானது. எனவே கேரட் இனிப்பு செய்முறையை கண்டிப்பாக பாருங்கள். கேரட் டெசர்ட் ரெசிபிகள் | இந்த கேரட் டிலைட் ரெசிபியை பகிர மறக்காதீர்கள் by indian Recipes tamil | Indian recipes tamil | அபியின் செய்முறை

Ingredients:
Carrot - 500 gms
Water - 500 ml
Corn Flour - 3 tbsp
Sugar Powder - 1/2 cup

* தேவையான பொருட்கள்:
கேரட் - 500 கிராம்
தண்ணீர் - 500 மிலி
சோள மாவு - 3 டீஸ்பூன்
சர்க்கரை தூள் - 1/2 கப்

snippet.title: बिना दाल भिगोए मूंग दाल की पकोङी बनाने का ऐसा नया तरीका पहले कभी ना देखा होगाCrispy Moong Dal Pakodi
snippet.description:
बिना दाल भिगोए मूंग दाल की पकोङी बनाने का ऐसा नया तरीका पहले कभी ना देखा होगाCrispy Moong Dal Pakodi

#MoongDalPakodiRecipe#CrispyPakodi#NirmlaNehraSnacksRecipes

Ingredients:-

Moong Dal-2 cup
Green Chilli-2-3
Ginger-1 inch
Coriander Seeds-1 tbsp
Cumin Seeds-1/2 tbsp
Fennel Seeds-1/2 tbsp
Asafoetida-2 pinch 
Black Pepper-1/2 tbsp
Gram Flour-1/2 cup
Curd-1/3 cup
Salt-to taste
Coriander Leaves
Garlic Chutney-1-2 tbsp
Oil-for frying

For Chutney:-
Soaked Kashmiri Red Chilli-7-8
Garlic Cloves-10-12
Fresh Coconut-1/2 cup
Dry Mango Powder-1 tbsp
Salt-to taste

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 07 Teaser - 12th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 07 Teaser - 12th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

#yumnazaidi 
#wahajali

snippet.title: Paresh Rawal Comedy - चिट्टी के चचेरे भाई औकात भूल गया, ऊंट की गर्दन खुजायेगा तू | Scene Compilation
snippet.description:
Janardhan Wishvanbhar Rane, a widower, has spent his life bringing up his two kids Chirag and Gaurav. Now when the two have grown up, Gaurav takes up his father's responsibility. They manage the household chores and their business as well. One day Gaurav meets his college friend Sheekha Kapoor, who lives with her guardian Anuradha who was Janardan's first love. Gaurav and Sheekha come to know about their past relationship. Now Gaurav wants his father to marry Anuradha.

Movie - Mere Baap Pehle Aap
Starcast - Akshaye Khanna, Paresh Rawal, Genelia D'Souza, Rajpal Yadav, Archana Puran Singh
Director - Priyadarshan

#merebaappehleaap #comedyscenes #pareshrawalcomedy

जनार्दन विश्वनभर राणे, एक विधुर, ने अपना जीवन अपने दो बच्चों चिराग और गौरव को पालने में बिताया है। अब जब दोनों बड़े हो गए हैं तो गौरव ने अपने पिता की जिम्मेदारी उठा ली है। वे घर का काम और अपना व्यवसाय भी संभालती हैं। एक दिन गौरव अपनी कॉलेज की दोस्त शिखा कपूर से मिलता है, जो अपनी अभिभावक अनुराधा के साथ रहती है, जो जनार्दन का पहला प्यार थी। गौरव और शिखा को अपने पिछले रिश्ते के बारे में पता चल जाता है। अब गौरव चाहता है कि उसके पिता अनुराधा से शादी कर लें।

फिल्म - मेरे बाप पहले आप
स्टारकास्ट - अक्षय खन्ना, परेश रावल, जेनेलिया डिसूजा, राजपाल यादव, अर्चना पूरन सिंह
निर्देशक - प्रियदर्शन

snippet.title: Jetha ने लिया Iyer से कटी पतंग का बदला | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Makar Sankranti Special
snippet.description:
All the residents of Gokhuldham enjoy the festival of Makar Sakranti, and they all fly the kites and enjoy. Their enjoyment pauses when Abdul informs them all about Pappu don. He has ordered that no one but his son will fly the kite. What will be everyone's reaction to this? Will they all get scared or will fight with him? Watch the full episode to know.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi
Episode - 523

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to Sony SAB Channel:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.description:
Champak, a theatre owner, is in need of an actress and his employees, Bunty and Babla, help him in his search. They get into trouble after their bag is switched with another one containing drugs.

Movie - Bhagam Bhag
Starcast: Akshay Kumar, Govinda, Paresh Rawal, Lara Dutta, Rajpal Yadav, Jackie Shroff , Arbaaz Khan, Shakti Kapoor
Director - Priyadarshan
Producer - Sunil Shetty, Dhilin Mehta
Cinematography - Jeeva
Editor - Arun Kumar

एक थियेटर मालिक चंपक को एक अभिनेत्री की जरूरत है और उसके कर्मचारी, बंटी और बाबला, उसकी खोज में उसकी मदद करते हैं। जब उनका बैग दूसरे ड्रग्स वाले बैग से बदल जाता है तो वे मुश्किल में पड़ जाते हैं।

snippet.title: AHIMSA Official Trailer | Teja | RP Patnaik | Kiran | Abhiram | Geethika | Rajat Bedi | Sada
snippet.description:
Watch & Enjoy : -- AHIMSA Official Trailer | Teja | RP Patnaik | Kiran | Abhiram | Geethika | Rajat Bedi | Sada

#AHIMSA  #AHIMSATrailer  #Teja #RPPatnaik #Kiran #Geethika #RajatBedi #Sada  

Director Teja, Anandi Arts Creations’ AHIMSA Shoot Wrapped Up

Director Teja has the calibre to deliver blockbusters with stars as well as upcoming actors. He indeed introduced many actors with his films and some of them become stars. He has proved numerous times that content is the king and films with good content do wonders at box office.

Teja is now introducing another debutant Abhiram as a hero with a youthful entertainer Ahimsa. This is going to be perfect Teja mark movie with the story incorporated with all the commercial ingredients.

P Kiran is producing the movie under Anandi Art Creations. Geethika has played Abhiram’s love interest, wherein Sada and Kamal Kamaraju will be seen in vital roles.

The film’s pre-look generated lots of curiosity on the film. It also gave an impression that Ahimsa will be high on action. Since the film’s shoot is wrapped up, the team will be kick-starting the promotional activities.

RP Patnaik who provided numerous chartbuster albums has scored music for the film. Teja, Anandi Arts Creations, and RP Patnaik have joined forces again after Nuvvu Nenu to deliver another musical blockbuster.

snippet.title: Shaakuntalam Official Trailer - Telugu | Samantha, Dev Mohan | Gunasekhar | Feb 17, 2023 Release
snippet.description:
Shaakuntalam Official Trailer - Telugu | Samantha, Dev Mohan | Gunasekhar | Feb 17, 2023 Release

Shaakuntalam Movie also in 3D, Written & Directed by Gunasekhar, Presented by Dil Raju under Sri Venkateswara Creations in collaboration with Gunaa Teamworks, Produced by Neelima Guna.

The massively mounted film Shaakuntalam based on internationally acclaimed Kalidasa’s Sanskrit play ‘Abhijnana Shakuntalam’ is all set to release in Hindi, Telugu, Tamil, Malayalam & Kannada.  The story of Shaakuntalam revolves around the epic love story of Shakuntala and King Dushyant from Mahabharata, portrayed by Samantha and Dev Mohan.

The film is helmed by supremely proficient, Director Gunasekhar and marks a whimsical tale of love set in the Kashyapa Kanumalu (Kashmir), the grandeur and splendour of Dushyant’s Puru Dynasty making the film extremely exceptional.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3666 - 12 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3666: Party Sharty Ka Nateeja
--------------------------------------------------------
Even though Bagha is taken to society by all the Gokuldham men, his peculiar conduct persists because of his intoxication. Bagha declines to take the medications when Dr. Hathi brings them out of his office. In an effort to get Bagha to agree to take the medication, Bhide amuses him by making amusing impersonations. Bagha warns everyone that if he is made to take the pills, he will depart in Sodhi's jeep. Bagha refuses to take the tablets. Alarmed, the women of Gokuldham descend to look about. Bagha ascends the balcony and moves closer to the edge. Everyone is concerned that he might lose his balance. Stay tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3666, 12 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000204229

snippet.description:
#DalKhichdi #MakarSankrantiRecipe #pressurecooker #khichdi  #unique #healthy 

INGREDINETS TO MAKE THE RECIPE:
1 Cup Dhuli Moong Dal 
1 Cup Short Grain Rice (i have use sona masoori)
VEGGIES :
1/2 Gobhi 
1/2 Cup Peas
1 Carrot 
7 - 8 Beans 
1 Big Potatoes 
Desi Ghee 
1 tsp Cumin Seeds 
2 Tbsp Salt 
1/2 tsp Haldi Powder 
6 Cups 

INGREDIENTS TO MAKE MASALA

2 Tbsp Coriander Powder 
1 Tbsp Jeera 
1 tsp Salt 
1/2 tsp Ajwain 
1 tsp Black Peppercorns 
2 Tbsp Anardana 
1 Tbsp Amchur Powder 
1 Tbsp Kala Namak 
1 Tbsp Garam Masala 
1 Tbsp Kasuri methi 
1 Tbsp Spicy Red Chilli Powder 

INGREDIENTS FOR TADKA 
1 Tbsp Desi Ghee 
1 Pinch Hing 
3 - 4 Chopped Garlic 
1 tsp Mustard Seeds 
1 tsp Cumin Seeds 
 5 -6  Curry Patta 
2 Dried Chillies

VEGGIES :

1 Carrot 
7 - 8 Beans 
1 Big Potatoes 
Desi Ghee 
1 tsp Cumin Seeds 
2 Tbsp Salt 
1/2 tsp Haldi Powder 
6 Cups

2 Dried Chillies

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3667 - 13 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3667: Bagha Ki Zidd
--------------------------------------------------------
Bagha refuses to step off the balcony, and the people of Gokuldham are concerned about him. Nattu Kaka tells Bagha that his actions are unjustified because they are causing unnecessary pain to the innocent Gokuldham dwellers. Jetha speaks about the delivery of his order to Bagha, which ends up disturbing him more. Babita tells Jetha not to discuss the job in this delicate situation. Jetha explains to Babita that he deliberately talked about work because Bagha is very professional and this could distract her spirit from Bawri. Will it really change Bagha's mindset?  Stay tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3667, 13 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000204411

snippet.title: क्या Thapki को पहचान पाएगा Bihaan? | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 591
snippet.description:
To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

As fate would have it, Bihaan bumps into Thapki once again at the school basketball court. On the persistence of Tina, Bihaan introduces himself to Thapki. But he is taken aback on knowing her name and walks away. Will he recall anything?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

Radhakrishn Raasleela- part 267 | Krishn laute Dwarka  | राधाकृष्ण | Radhakrishn

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!


Jaanne ke liye dekhiye #RadhaKrishn, Somvaar se Shanivaar, shaam 7.30 baje, sirf #StarBharat par. Krishn aur Radha ki leelaon se judde rehne ke liye hamein follow kariye Instagram, Facebook aur YouTube par!

snippet.title: Kya Sahi, Kya Nahi - Maruti Jimny 4x4 India | First Look
snippet.description: Maruti Suzuki Jimny 5-door has finally come to India, as its bookings open today. Upon its launch, it will rival Mahindra Thar thanks to its 4x4 system and body-on-frame architecture. It gets 1.5L K15B engine, which will be offered with a 5-speed manual and 4-speed automatic. Though the prices haven’t been revealed yet, we expect it to come at Rs 12 lakh.

snippet.title: Veera Simha Reddy Trailer | Nandamuri Balakrishna | Gopichand Malineni | Thaman S | Shruti Haasan
snippet.description:

snippet.description:

#thunivu #ajith #hvinoth 

Visit us at http://filmcompanion.in

Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/c/FilmCompanionSouth

Follow Us On:
https://www.facebook.com/filmcompanion
https://www.twitter.com/filmcompanion
http://instagram.com/filmcompanion

About Film Companion South:
Film Companion South is a division of Film Companion, founded by film critic and author Anupama Chopra. Apart from film reviews and articles, Film Companion South, with programs in Tamil, Malayalam, Telugu, and Kannada, specializes in conducting in-depth interviews with film personalities which include the likes of Kamal Hassan, Mani Ratnam, Academy Award-winner AR Rahman, Vetrimaaran, Dhanush, Yash, Sruthi Hariharan, Mahesh Babu, NTR Jr, Samantha, Aishwarya Rajesh, Ramya Krishnan, Prithviraj, Anjali Menon, Mysskin, Gautam Vasudev Menon, Rajamouli, Ram Charan, Yash, Prashanth Neel, Venkat Prabhu, Nelson, Sivakarthikeyan, Rakshit Shetty and many more. The channel has also hosted shows which open up the lesser-known facets of filmmaking with conversations with PC Sreeram, Ravi Varman, Rajiv Menon, Thota Tharani, and Academy Award-winner Resul Pookutty. In other words, Film Companion South is for those who love their cinema and are unapologetic about it.

Judwa behene Divya aur Drishti ko apne janam se mila hai shakti ka vardaan. Drishti bhavishya kaal ko dekh sakti hai aur Divya ussey badal sakti hai. Inke mata pita ne apni jaan ka balidaan dekar bachaya dono beheno ko par bichad gaye bachpan mai Divya aur Drishti. Alag alag parivaaron mai pale bade par ek doosre ko dhundhte rahe.
